imdb.plot outline: Yolanda Acosta is an attractive and intelligent woman capable of breaking the law just to protect her beloved daughter Cristina, but destiny makes her the lover of Benedicto Suárez alias El Centauro, one of the most important drug traffickers in the country who will also end up being her worst nightmare.
